-- Beijing's New Home Sales Dropped 65% by Area From Year Earlier Last Month
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-17T06:57:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/beijing-s-new-home-sales-dropped-65-by-area-from-year-earlier-last-month.html

          
          
             Sales of new homes in Beijing by
floorspace dropped 65 percent in May from a year earlier and 48
percent from April to 618,000 square meters, the Beijing
statistics bureau said on its website today.  
 The price of new housing in May rose 0.9 percent from
April, the bureau said, without giving a figure.  
          
          


  


        